		<div class='show ' id='content_wrapper'>
						<h1 id="firstHeading">IBM Personal Computer</h1>			
<div class="dablink">"IBM PC" redirects here. For general IBM-like PCs, see <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/IBM_PC_compatible" title="IBM PC compatible">IBM PC compatible</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox hproduct vevent" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<caption class="fn summary" style="">IBM PC (model 5150)</caption>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;">
<a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042,_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Bundesarchiv B 145 Bild-F077869-0042, Jugend-Computerschule mit IBM-PC.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg/250px-Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg" width="250" height="165" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg/375px-Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg/500px-Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F077869-0042%2C_Jugend-Computerschule_mit_IBM-PC.jpg 2x"></a><br><span style="">IBM Personal Computer model 5150 with IBM <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Color_Graphics_Adapter" title="Color Graphics Adapter">CGA</a> monitor (model number 5153), IBM PC keyboard, <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_IBM_products#IBM_PC_components_and_peripherals" title="List of IBM products">IBM 5152</a> printer and paper stand.</span>
